## Summary by CodeRabbit

* **New Features**
  * Added decorator-style annotations (e.g., @name, @name(value), @name('''...''')) that can be placed before pair keys across params, headers, form/multipart fields, vars, and asserts; parsed outputs include an annotations field when present, and serialization emits annotations (preserving formatting for disabled items and selecting quotes to avoid escapes).

* **Tests**
  * Added comprehensive tests and fixture covering parsing, serialization, quoting, multiline/special-character edge cases, placement variants, disabled pairs, and roundtrip equality.
